  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704980/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1728340014\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704980/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1728340014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704980/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1728340014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you like puzzles and a beautiful story, this is the right game for you, Jigsaw Puzzle Jack and the Beanstalk is a minimalist game with 5 difficulty levels (64, 144, 289, 484 and 784 pieces).<br><br>8 different puzzles with original art.<br><br>Automatically saved parts so you never lose your progress.<br><br>5 difficulty levels (64, 144, 289, 484 and 784 pieces).<br><br>With several backgrounds to change.<br><br>Zoom and move the scene, highlight the edge pieces, mix the remaining pieces, visualize the scene.<br><br>Relaxing music and atmosphere.<br> <br>Minimalist.<br><br><br>Game Tips :)<br><br><br><strong>Move Piece</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704980/extras/eebe426c16b991b1b19d796aae0fd170.poster.avif?t=1728340014\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704980/extras/eebe426c16b991b1b19d796aae0fd170.webm?t=1728340014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704980/extras/eebe426c16b991b1b19d796aae0fd170.mp4?t=1728340014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Zoom</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" au